            text={"I thrive in organised chaos. Love my titles big and bold and putting text sideways. My drawings show my love for contrast, which is why ink is my favourite material to use. I don't have a favourite colour but somehow end up using red as an accent colour in too many of my designs and drawings. "}
          />
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="about__education">
        <div class="about__education__container">
          <PictureSelected
            extraClass="about__education__img"
            title="a drawing of a fish in a blue fishbowl with white bubbles"
            img={artfish}
            width="754"
            height="484"
          />
          <div class="devine-shirt__container about__education__shirt">
            <Picture
              src={devineshirt}
              alt="a black shirt with the Devine logo"
              class="devine-shirt"
            />
            <p>Devine-Uniform</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>my education</h2>
          <p class="education__p">
            I studied science with 8 hours of math in high school, where I
            discovered my love for programming anew after using scratch when I
            was younger.
          </p>
          <p class="education__p">
            I stumbled upon Devine by accident and immediately knew this would
            be the school for me. <em
              >Devine balances all the areas I wanted to study further: the
              creative the logical and the human.</em
            > In my third year at the Devine I got the change to spend a semester
            at <em> Hanyang in south-Korea.</em>
          </p>
          <p class="education__p">
            When I was twelve I started going to the Sint-Lucas Academie, an art
            academy in Gent. After seven years in the kids program I started the
            two year initian course. I completed the initiation course and got
            the degree when I was 19.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>
  </div>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
